These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, lemonade
There 3 different types of food: apple, plum, zucchini
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, animation
There are 3 different nationalities: british, pakistani, argentine
3 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, frog
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, ship, motorbike
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating plum is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the british##1
5. the pakistani is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person eating apple is between the owner of the turtle and the person eating plum##2
8. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | hot-chocolate      | juice      |
| Food          | plum   | apple   | zucchini       |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | comedy | disaster    |
| Nationality   | argentine  | british    | pakistani    |
| Pet           | rat    | frog    | turtle |
| Transport     | ship  | motorbike     | taxi        |

