.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: kale, strawberry, blueberry
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy, epic
There are 3 different nationalities: british, indonesian, egyptian
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, horse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, baseball
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the person eating blueberry is between the egyptian and the person drinking soy-milk##2
7. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching epic movies and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate        | soy-milk      |
| Food          | strawberry    | blueberry       | kale  |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | spy | martial-arts    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | british   | indonesian    |
| Pet           | frog      | ferret  | horse      |
| Sport         | baseball    | lacrosse      | sailing |

