There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, british, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: lizard, hedgehog, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, trike
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the nigerian and the owner of the lizard##2
2. the british is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the argentine is the argentine##1
4. the owner of the mouse is the fan of salsa##1
5. the british is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person eating strawberry##2
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
8. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | strawberry  | peach    | papaya   |
| Hobby         | reading | video-games | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep       | salsa    | r&b |
| Nationality   | nigerian    | british  | argentine  |
| Pet           | hedgehog     | mouse   | lizard       |
| Transport     | roller | motorbike     | trike       |

