The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, animation, sports
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, country, techno
3 different pets are kept: mouse, hamster, horse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing, skiing
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, skateboard, bus
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the train and the owner of the horse##2
3. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of country##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of punk##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | sprite   | cola      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | sports  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | country  | techno        |
| Pet           | horse       | hamster   | mouse |
| Sport         | surfing      | skiing | ice-hockey   |
| Transport     | skateboard   | bus     | train |

 